{"tid":958610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"急診室怪奇物語　巴斯光年、拐杖糖被塞入體內","createTime":"2018-12-28T03:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T12:34:42.000Z","uid":121473,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"25b0f49ab7fe0ca36dae61d0190fb6ba3cee517f","tid":958610,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:14:32.000Z","msg":"美國聯邦機構列出數據，指當地急診室每年都收到不少個案，是有人將異物放入體內無法自己取出而求診。玩具如巴斯光年模型、啤酒瓶、聖誕「拐杖糖」，都是醫師曾從人體內取出的異物，而直腸是最常見被放入異物的地方。<br />\n <br />\n美國消費品安全委員會（Consumer Product Safety Commission）2017年的數據顯示，直腸是最多人藏入異物的地方，其他的地方包括耳道、眼睛、鼻孔、喉嚨和生殖器官。<br />\n <br />\n醫師從病人直腸取出的異物包括7盎司的啤酒瓶、噴霧罐、雪茄管、藥瓶、聖誕掛飾等，從X光片中可見，體積不小的異物被整個放入體內。而它們被放入體內的原因亦十分離奇，包括「跳上床，床上有支牙刷，牙刷插入了病人的直腸」、「坐上沙發，但不慎坐上了原子筆，原子筆卡在直腸」等等。<br />\n <br />\n另外，亦有病人耳道被塞入玩具老鼠、鼻孔放入游泳浮條、小型收音機卡住喉嚨。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GVsVMTK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGVsVMTK.jpg&h=2b7707f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rzqz2r4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frzqz2r4.jpg&h=cea2faaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8jw4Fq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8jw4Fq.jpg&h=95a6dd73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bpbobkr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBpbobkr.jpg&h=ad8936b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181228/1491044/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181228%2F1491044%2F&d=eweu%2BmSeRtL8pKBwkrlkFRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=5f5861a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181228%2F1491044%2F&h=f424d448\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181228/1491044/</a>"}